sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant UI as Frontend (React)
    participant API as Express Server
    participant Orchestrator as Detection Service
    participant Gemini as Gemini 2.5 Flash
    participant Verify as Verification Pass
    participant Priority as Review Priority Engine

    User->>UI: Uploads Document
    UI->>API: POST /upload (File Blob)
    
    API->>Orchestrator: Extract Text & Start Pipeline
    Orchestrator->>Gemini: Prompt + Document Text
    
    alt Success
        Gemini-->>Orchestrator: JSON Detections (Offsets & Confidence)
    else Timeout / Rate Limit / Hallucination
        Orchestrator-->>API: Throw Exception
        API-->>UI: 500 Error (Provider Failed)
        UI-->>User: Display Error Banner
    end
    
    Orchestrator->>Verify: Validate Schema & Offsets
    Verify->>Verify: Auto-Repair Offsets
    Verify->>Verify: Regex Gap Detection
    
    Verify->>Priority: Validated Entities
    Priority->>Priority: Apply 6 Heuristic Rules
    Priority->>Priority: Categorize (HIGH, STD, LOW)
    
    Priority-->>API: Enriched Response Array
    API-->>UI: Return JSON Payload
    
    UI->>UI: Render Document with Interactive Popovers
    UI->>UI: Render Sidebar sorted by Priority
    
    User->>UI: Review High-Risk Items
    User->>UI: Click Approve
    UI-->>User: Final Clearance
